title: [FSX/P3D] FlyTampa - Copenhagen v1.4 (Working Torrent)
description:
Thanks to duffis nuts torrent, I went and got it myself and wanted to share. Included in the zip are the instructions, serial, and the v4 update. Remember to seed people. Thanks!!!


Install Notes: Run the FlyTampa-Config-Tool and make sure to select "North-East winds" under Copenhagen Airport operations. You can change that option again after applying the Update files.
Extract ZIP to Prepar3D/FlyTampa/
Delete: Prepar3D/FlyTampa/Copenhagen/scenery/ 5 files named ******_papi.bgl
